Our Super Chat Proceeds from this Livestream Went to The Red Cross and The Hurricane Harvey Relief Fund. YOU CAN STILL HELP by DONATING to These Organizations:

The Red Cross ►► https://goo.gl/Ex8KNk
Hurricane Harvey Relief Fund ►► https://goo.gl/Jw3Z8Q

After the destruction and floods caused by Hurricane Harvey, we decided the Theorist Community should do its best to help out. One good way to do this is by donating to help catastrophe relief efforts. In this episode, Super Chat was enabled in order to raise money for this cause. 100% of our Super Chat Proceeds will go to help fund relief efforts working to save lives and rebuild infrastructure in Texas. For this Special Stream, we played UNDERTALE since we've been asked to play it more than any other game on GTLive. Enjoy this special charity event and help us help Texans affected by the storm!
